data.description: Jumping out of HGTV, this home will not disappoint, primed and waiting for its next owner. Its expansive open floor design creates a sense of boundless space, complemented by wood-like tile flooring. The updated kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, and enhanced by new light fixtures, is a focal point of modern luxury. Sunlight floods through the ample large windows, illuminating every corner naturally. Plus, the home's garage is equipped with an electric vehicle charger for added convenience. Step outside to the generously sized backyard, complete with a concrete patio, perfect for hosting gatherings. Conveniently located with quick access to I-35, 410, 1604, and Wurzbach Parkway to get anywhere in San Antonio, this home is truly the coolest house in the neighborhood. Don't miss the chance to experience this exceptional home firsthand. Schedule your viewing today!
